WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.470
Good morning family, praise the Lord!

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.630
How are you all doing today? Well, thank you

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:06.710
for joining me. You know, I was praying

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:09.110
this evening and the Lord spoke to

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:12.110
me and said, 'Brandon, 2025 is going to

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.509
be a good year for the

00:00:14.509 --> 00:00:14.519
believers.'I

00:00:14.519 --> 00:00:17.269
was looking over in the

00:00:17.279 --> 00:00:18.750
spirit and the Lord was allowing me to

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:21.590
see

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:24.790
the outpouring of

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:27.509
healings, the demonstrations, and the

00:00:27.509 --> 00:00:27.519
manifestations

00:00:27.519 --> 00:00:30.349
of the Father. You all,

00:00:30.359 --> 00:00:32.510
we're about to see some of the most

00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:36.709
amazing things. I'm telling you, our

00:00:36.709 --> 00:00:36.719
forefathers—like

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:40.510
even 200

00:00:40.510 --> 00:00:40.520
or

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:42.029
300 years ago—the people who were

00:00:42.039 --> 00:00:44.869
looking forward to the Lord Jesus coming

00:00:44.879 --> 00:00:46.510
and thought he was coming in their

00:00:46.510 --> 00:00:46.520
timeframe,

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:49.670
folks, we're about to see the

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:53.270
Lord Jesus come. We're going to see a

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:56.189
major harvest of souls. I know I keep

00:00:56.199 --> 00:00:58.110
telling you all this, and I've said it

00:00:58.120 --> 00:00:59.470
over and over; I probably sound like

00:00:59.470 --> 00:00:59.480
a

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:03.430
broken record, but I need you

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:07.390
to know it. I need you to have a deep

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:10.109
revelation that God is about to do

00:01:10.119 --> 00:01:11.670
something, because he keeps telling

00:01:11.670 --> 00:01:11.680
me,

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:14.350
'Brandon, I'm about to show up and

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:17.270
show off in your life. I want you to

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:20.270
believe me for bigger.'This is the second

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:22.910
time this week he said that. We are on

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:26.429
the countdown: 5, 4, 3,

00:01:26.439 --> 00:01:31.030
2, 1, liftoff! I'm telling you, a

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:35.350
great move of God is about to hit this

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:38.270
land like you have never seen. I'm telling you:

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:40.950
exceedingly abundantly above all that

00:01:40.960 --> 00:01:44.109
you dare ask or think. It's time to

00:01:44.119 --> 00:01:47.350
believe God for

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:51.469
bigger. Stretch your faith to

00:01:51.479 --> 00:01:53.910
believe exceedingly abundantly above all

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:56.709
that you dare ask or think.

00:01:56.719 --> 00:01:58.990
He said, 'Brandon, it's going to

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:00.749
be about the thinking.'I said this

00:02:00.759 --> 00:02:03.310
yesterday, but

00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:05.270
it just keeps bubbling

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:08.070
inside of me,

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:10.150
just believing. I went to a Christmas

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:12.190
party today and it was all I could do. I

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:14.470
was sitting at the front,

00:02:14.470 --> 00:02:14.480
and

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:16.150
it's probably because it's a

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:18.670
prayer

00:02:18.670 --> 00:02:18.680
church—you

00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:20.550
know, our church has a lot of

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.430
intercessory prayer that goes forth out of

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:22.440
there—but

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:24.430
I was sitting toward the

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:26.470
front where they had the dinner, and

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:28.390
I felt like

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:30.350
travail was

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:31.830
hitting me in the middle of the

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:33.710
Christmas party. People were playing

00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:36.309
games and everything, and I'm looking,

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:38.150
going, 'My goodness, I just feel like I

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:40.910
could weep because of the

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:43.110
intercession coming up out of my

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:45.949
spirit to intercede for the lost and

00:02:45.959 --> 00:02:48.750
for what's

00:02:48.750 --> 00:02:48.760
coming.'When

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:51.470
I came home,

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:53.790
I started watching Billy Burke.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:56.110
I told my wife,

00:02:56.120 --> 00:02:57.509
'I want to hear this sermon

00:02:57.509 --> 00:02:57.519
from

00:02:57.519 --> 00:02:58.869
Billy

00:02:58.869 --> 00:02:58.879
Burke,'because

00:02:58.879 --> 00:03:00.270
it was a healing thing. He was

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:03.750
teaching healing and he

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:06.670
just fans my flame. The words

00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:09.990
he speaks

00:03:09.990 --> 00:03:10.000
inspire

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.949
me, and I just want to stay

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:14.670
inspired. People were asking in the

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:16.670
comment section—my son told me and my

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:18.149
wife told me from the emails—people are

00:03:18.159 --> 00:03:21.030
saying, 'How, Brandon, do we have an

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:23.470
intimate relationship with the Father?

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:25.509
How do we get

00:03:25.509 --> 00:03:25.519
there?'When

00:03:25.519 --> 00:03:28.509
Diana shared the word

00:03:28.519 --> 00:03:31.910
she had from the Lord,

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:33.830
it challenged a lot of you, and

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:36.750
rightfully so. It challenged me and it

00:03:36.760 --> 00:03:39.110
challenged her. It wasn't

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:41.030
just that he was speaking it to us and

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:43.190
we let it fall on

00:03:43.190 --> 00:03:43.200
deaf

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:45.190
ears.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:48.149
He was talking to us too,

00:03:48.159 --> 00:03:52.149
because we need to come up

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:55.789
higher. Diana and I have talked

00:03:55.799 --> 00:03:58.149
about that word a lot lately.

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:06.069
Going to a place of

00:04:06.079 --> 00:04:09.149
intimacy with the Father

00:04:09.159 --> 00:04:14.149
is not a hard thing. We make it hard

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:17.069
because we think God is way out there. Of

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:19.749
course, God is a holy God, a

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:22.150
big God, the ultimate

00:04:22.150 --> 00:04:22.160
in

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:24.469
everything, but he's small enough to live

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:28.030
in each one of us. It's like the

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:30.550
Imperials sang: 'My God is a big

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.870
God who walks among the

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:35.430
mountains, but he's small enough to live

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:39.189
in me.'God is small enough to live in

00:04:39.199 --> 00:04:43.430
you. He lives on the inside of us, and we

00:04:43.440 --> 00:04:46.350
make it difficult whenever we have

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:49.990
all these religious thoughts like

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.510
Pharisees. We think

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:55.270
God doesn't want to spend time with

00:04:55.270 --> 00:04:55.280
us.

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:57.029
We have all these stupid thoughts

00:04:57.039 --> 00:04:58.510
because the devil tries to put those

00:04:58.520 --> 00:05:02.110
negative words in; he comes like a

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:04.430
roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:06.909
He's looking for those he can

00:05:06.919 --> 00:05:09.909
pick

00:05:09.909 --> 00:05:09.919
off—the

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:12.070
ones who are

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:15.189
lukewarm, cold,

00:05:15.189 --> 00:05:15.199
or

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:17.550
not hot.

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:19.110
Like Billy Burke said tonight when I

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:21.430
was watching

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:21.440
him,

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:24.670
there's a river of water that

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:28.749
flows out of us. Have you

00:05:28.759 --> 00:05:30.909
ever seen a fire hose when

00:05:30.909 --> 00:05:30.919
the

00:05:30.919 --> 00:05:32.790
fire department

00:05:32.790 --> 00:05:32.800
is

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:35.270
putting out a big fire? A major

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:38.150
fire hose will knock you down. The

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:40.150
devil is looking to see if there is a

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:43.070
major fire hose, a major river flowing

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:45.390
out of you. When

00:05:45.390 --> 00:05:45.400
you are

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:47.029
standing there, he's looking

00:05:47.039 --> 00:05:49.830
to see if you have it or not,

00:05:49.840 --> 00:05:52.909
because any Christian who is on fire,

00:05:52.919 --> 00:05:54.550
he's going to run away from.

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:57.189
James says that if we submit

00:05:57.189 --> 00:05:57.199
ourselves

00:05:57.199 --> 00:06:00.309
unto God and resist the devil,

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:04.029
he will flee in terror. So he's looking

00:06:04.029 --> 00:06:04.039
for

00:06:04.039 --> 00:06:07.870
who has that fire, who has that

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:10.909
inward knowing of who they are in

00:06:10.909 --> 00:06:10.919
Christ—that

00:06:10.919 --> 00:06:13.070
you can do all things through Christ who

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:16.110
strengthens you. He's

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:18.710
out there,

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:21.309
his eyes roaming to and fro,

00:06:21.319 --> 00:06:23.909
and he's going, 'I want to see who I can

00:06:23.909 --> 00:06:23.919
devour.'But

00:06:23.919 --> 00:06:26.430
he can't devour the one

00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:26.440
whose

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:30.710
foundation

00:06:30.710 --> 00:06:30.720
and

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:34.110
house is built on the solid rock.

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:37.230
He knows whom he can devour and

00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:37.240
whom

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:39.029
he can't; that's why he's

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:41.550
seeking, because there are some folks he

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:43.749
knows he can't mess with. Those are

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:46.309
the ones who are on fire for Jesus. So

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:49.350
how do you get on fire for Jesus? He made

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:52.029
it so a child can have a relationship

00:06:52.039 --> 00:06:55.070
with him. He made it so every

00:06:55.070 --> 00:06:55.080
born-again

00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:58.189
Christian has the ability. We

00:06:58.199 --> 00:07:00.710
all have 24 hours in a day,

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:03.189
seven days a week.

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:05.350
Not one of us has any more and not one

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.830
has anything less, but everyone has

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:08.950
a

00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:11.510
choice of how much time they're going to

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:14.749
spend with him today. You may say, 'Well,

00:07:14.759 --> 00:07:17.230
I'm so busy. I've got to go to the gym, I've

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:19.430
got to go to work, I've got to come home

00:07:19.430 --> 00:07:19.440
and

00:07:19.440 --> 00:07:21.950
watch my favorite TV

00:07:21.950 --> 00:07:21.960
program.'Then

00:07:21.960 --> 00:07:24.430
you have some people

00:07:24.430 --> 00:07:24.440
who

00:07:24.440 --> 00:07:25.909
go to the gym and look like

00:07:25.919 --> 00:07:28.469
Arnold Schwarzenegger,

00:07:28.479 --> 00:07:31.869
or any athlete,

00:07:31.879 --> 00:07:34.550
but everyone has a choice of

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:36.950
how they want to spend their time. If

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:39.150
you want to be a spiritual giant, you

00:07:39.150 --> 00:07:39.160
have

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:41.629
to do what a spiritual giant does. You've

00:07:41.639 --> 00:07:43.510
got to get in

00:07:43.510 --> 00:07:43.520
the

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:46.270
word. Everybody has the opportunity to

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:48.550
get in the word. You can get your Bible

00:07:48.560 --> 00:07:50.670
out, look at those scriptures, read a

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:53.189
couple of passages, and memorize

00:07:53.189 --> 00:07:53.199
them.

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:57.390
It's not going to be

00:07:57.400 --> 00:08:00.869
a microwave; it's going to be a

00:08:00.869 --> 00:08:00.879
slow-cook

00:08:00.879 --> 00:08:03.830
oven.

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.990
Find one or two scriptures

00:08:05.990 --> 00:08:06.000
and

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:07.710
memorize them over the week.

00:08:07.710 --> 00:08:07.720
If you memorize ten

00:08:07.720 --> 00:08:10.790
scriptures over the

00:08:13.599 --> 00:08:16.350
year,

00:08:20.840 --> 00:08:23.270
think

00:08:23.280 --> 00:08:25.749
about the math on that.

00:08:25.749 --> 00:08:25.759
If

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:28.749
you get

00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:30.390
those down

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:32.149
inside

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:34.509
of your heart within a two-year period,

00:08:34.519 --> 00:08:37.269
think about where you'll

00:08:37.279 --> 00:08:41.190
be. Praying in the spirit: I had a

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:42.909
counselor when I worked for

00:08:42.909 --> 00:08:42.919
Rhema

00:08:42.919 --> 00:08:44.990
Ministry. She said if you pray in the

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.990
spirit and talk in

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:50.070
tongues for 30 minutes a day,

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:52.750
your life will never be the same. Then

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:55.710
increase it to an hour.

00:08:57.560 --> 00:09:00.150
Brother Kenneth

00:09:00.150 --> 00:09:00.160
Hagin

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:01.990
talked about praying for an hour or two in

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.310
tongues,

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.910
in the

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:08.710
mornings and the evenings.

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.110
That's why I've tried to tell you all:

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:16.630
if your

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:19.870
flesh eats breakfast, lunch, and dinner,

00:09:19.880 --> 00:09:22.670
try to feed your spirit breakfast, lunch,

00:09:22.680 --> 00:09:25.870
and dinner.

00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:42.069
Feeding your spirit three times a day with

00:09:42.069 --> 00:09:42.079
small

00:09:42.079 --> 00:09:44.269
passages doesn't have to be

00:09:44.269 --> 00:09:44.279
reading

00:09:44.279 --> 00:09:46.790
the whole

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:48.949
Bible. People get on these

00:09:48.959 --> 00:09:50.509
religious kicks and say, 'I'm going to

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:52.590
read the Bible in a

00:09:52.590 --> 00:09:52.600
year.'Fine,

00:09:52.600 --> 00:09:54.350
but did you learn

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:58.230
anything? Did the word change you, or did

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:01.190
you just do it

00:10:01.190 --> 00:10:01.200
to

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:02.870
brag about it?

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:13.430
Find scriptures that will change

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:17.269
you. The

00:10:17.279 --> 00:10:20.870
Bible says, 'If ye abide in me and my words

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:23.630
remain in you, you shall ask what you

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:26.590
will and it shall be

00:10:26.590 --> 00:10:26.600
done.'If

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:28.350
you're getting that word down inside

00:10:28.360 --> 00:10:30.870
of you and feeding on it,

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:34.910
that's when your prayers get answered.

00:10:43.560 --> 00:10:46.030
If you're not

00:10:46.040 --> 00:10:48.150
getting your prayers answered, maybe it's

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:49.870
because you don't have enough word

00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:52.350
inside of you. The more word you

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:54.629
put on the inside, the more

00:10:54.639 --> 00:10:56.949
you're going to see things change,

00:10:56.959 --> 00:10:58.310
because that's when your prayers are

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:00.590
going to get answered. Prayer

00:11:00.590 --> 00:11:00.600
changes

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:03.110
things, but it's the scripture you

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.590
know that's going to change you.

00:11:07.880 --> 00:11:10.430
People say, 'I've got a

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:11.870
devil,'and

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:13.590
'I don't know how to get

00:11:13.590 --> 00:11:13.600
free.'The

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:16.910
Bible says you will know the

00:11:16.920 --> 00:11:19.949
truth and the truth will set you

00:11:19.959 --> 00:11:23.590
free. The more you get inside the word of

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:26.069
God, the more it's going to change you

00:11:26.079 --> 00:11:28.190
from glory to

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:30.550
glory. How do you become

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:32.870
intimate with the

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:35.069
Lord? You

00:11:35.079 --> 00:11:38.030
get intimate with the word. When

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:40.389
you get the word inside of you, your

00:11:40.399 --> 00:11:42.310
prayer life is going to change.

00:11:42.310 --> 00:11:42.320
Faith

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:45.069
comes

00:11:45.069 --> 00:11:45.079
by

00:11:47.670 --> 00:11:47.680
hearing,

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:50.310
and

00:11:50.310 --> 00:11:50.320
hearing

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:52.670
by

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:54.750
the word

00:11:54.760 --> 00:11:56.670
of

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:58.790
God.

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:00.790
Your faith

00:12:00.800 --> 00:12:03.750
is

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:06.310
going to

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:08.389
grow, you're going to be intimate with

00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:10.430
the Father, and it's going to change your

00:12:10.440 --> 00:12:12.949
life. The Bible says that his

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:15.350
sheep will hear his voice and a

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.990
stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:20.030
But you don't know that until you get

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:21.990
inside that word.

00:12:26.600 --> 00:12:30.470
Have a revelation of that.

